<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">4 * Aqualux Spa &amp; Suite Hotel</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Lake Garda</h2>
<br />
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/hotel-aqualux-spa-suite" title="Hotel Aqualux, Lake Garda"><img src="/media/13075260/piscina-pool_salina.jpg" alt="Swimming Pool, Hotel Aqualux" data-udi="umb://media/490e6438c16f480b8a58a2b4c70736f5" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Modern hotel with a plethora of different swimming pools and wellness facilities. 10 minutes from the centre of historic <a data-udi="umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59fcac55a66d4666ae4b0cca449364d1}" title="Bardolino">Bardolino</a>.</p>
