</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/bardolino/hotel-aqualux-spa-suite" title="Hotel Aqualux, Lake Garda"><strong>Book now &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
